		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Can the NES read 4 power pads using the 4-score or an NES satellite?
<br />
<br />If not, can it read 2 power pads?
<br />
<br />I know there are no games currently that will allow this, but I would like to develop one if it is possible.  
<br />
<br />Thanks.
<br />
<br />Dusty

		

