	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It looks like the power pad uses the same controller pins as the Zapper.  I remember the satellite had a switch to select zapper/controller, but I don't know if that would work with all 4 ports.  I only know of one game that uses 2 zappers, that's Chiller.
<br />
<br />But yeah, it could definitely use 2 power pads, plugged straight in.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
